    <item>
      <title>中国国家银行请求法院清算开发商世茂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/chinese-developer-shimao-receives-wind-up-petition-in-hong-kong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的中国开发商世茂集团控股有限公司正面临债权人中国建设银行（亚洲）股份有限公司的清算要求，这是迄今为止国有银行试图从陷入困境的开发商收回资金的最突出例子之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/chinese-developer-shimao-receives-wind-up-petition-in-hong-kong</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:55:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油集会因以色列撤出部分加沙军队而暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列表示将从加沙撤走部分军队后，油价从五个月高点下跌，交易员等待本周一系列市场报告，这些报告将提供供需概况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 23:26:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
